{
  "title": "IASA Opens Nominations for 2025 IMPACT Awards",
  "body": "<html><body><div class=\"ContentPanel\" id=\"mainContentWrapper\">\n<div data-height-offset=\"true\" id=\"masterMainBreadcrumb\"></div>\n<div id=\"ctl01_UserMessagesUpdatePanel\">\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"ctl01_TemplateBody_PublishUpdatePanel\">\n</div><div id=\"ctl01_TemplateBody_WebPartManager1___Drag\" style=\"display:none;position:absolute;z-index:32000;filter:alpha(opacity=75);\">\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-8\">\n<div class=\"ContentItemContainer\">\n<div class=\"WebPartZone\" id=\"WebPartZone1_Page1\">\n<div class=\"iMIS-WebPart\">\n<div class=\"ContentItemContainer\" id=\"ste_container_ciNewContentHtml_ccb9a62a66084dfebbcaa139af54f0ca\"><div id=\"ctl01_TemplateBody_WebPartManager1_gwpciNewContentHtml_ccb9a62a66084dfebbcaa139af54f0ca_ciNewContentHtml_ccb9a62a66084dfebbcaa139af54f0ca_Panel_NewContentHtml\">\n<h2>IASA Opens Nominations for 2025 IMPACT Awards</h2>\n<p>Nominations are now open for the 2025 IASA IMPACT Awards, which honor exceptional contributions to the insurance industry. Submissions are welcome from both members and non-members through March 28, 2025.<br/>\n<br/>\r\nAwards include the Industry Trailblazer Award for companies leading through innovation, service, sustainability, or strategy, as well as two individual honors: IASA Volunteer of the Year and Speaker/Educator of the Year. Winners will be announced at IASA Xchange™, June 8, 2025, in St. Louis.</p>\n<p><a class=\"btn TextButton PrimaryButton\" href=\"/common/Uploaded%20files/News/2025%20IASA%20IMPACT%20Award%20Press%20Release.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">View Press Release</a></p>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"ctl01_TemplateBody_ContentPage1_downloadContainer\" style=\"display:none;\">\n<input id=\"ctl01_TemplateBody_ContentPage1_HiddenDownloadPathField\" name=\"ctl01$TemplateBody$ContentPage1$HiddenDownloadPathField\" type=\"hidden\"/><input id=\"ctl01_TemplateBody_ContentPage1_downloadButton\" name=\"ctl01$TemplateBody$ContentPage1$downloadButton\" style=\"display:none\" type=\"submit\" value=\"Download Path\"/>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-4\">\n<div class=\"ContentItemContainer\">\n<div class=\"WebPartZone\" id=\"WebPartZone2_Page1\">\n<div class=\"iMIS-WebPart\">\n<div class=\"ContentItemContainer\" id=\"ste_container_ciNewContentHtml2_5713d1093b6c43679f6ace04238d9667\"><div id=\"ctl01_TemplateBody_WebPartManager1_gwpciNewContentHtml2_5713d1093b6c43679f6ace04238d9667_ciNewContentHtml2_5713d1093b6c43679f6ace04238d9667_Panel_NewContentHtml2\">\n<a href=\"/common/Uploaded%20files/News/2025%20IASA%20IMPACT%20Award%20Press%20Release.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/IASA/News/Call-Nominations-Awards-URL.jpg?version=358E69EA\"/></a>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"ctl01_TemplateBody_ContentPage2_downloadContainer\" style=\"display:none;\">\n<input id=\"ctl01_TemplateBody_ContentPage2_HiddenDownloadPathField\" name=\"ctl01$TemplateBody$ContentPage2$HiddenDownloadPathField\" type=\"hidden\"/><input id=\"ctl01_TemplateBody_ContentPage2_downloadButton\" name=\"ctl01$TemplateBody$ContentPage2$downloadButton\" style=\"display:none\" type=\"submit\" value=\"Download Path\"/>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div></body></html>",
